    <item>
      <title>中国将把香港、澳门游客免税限额提高一倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/china-to-double-duty-free-limit-for-visitors-to-hong-kong-macau</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自下周起，内地游客在香港和澳门可享受最高 15,000 元人民币（2,064 美元）的免税购物，约为当前限额的两倍，当局正努力帮助这些仍在努力从新冠疫情影响中全面恢复的城市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/china-to-double-duty-free-limit-for-visitors-to-hong-kong-macau</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:50:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
